HEADWORD: Anecdote
<hw>An"ec*dote</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>anecdote</ets>, fr. Gr. <?/ not published; <grk>'an</grk> priv. +
<?/ given out, <?/ to give out, to publish; <?/ out + <?/ to give. See
